      "abstract": "This bill makes technical corrections to conform existing law to the standards of the Delaware Legislative Drafting Manual, adds definitions for \u201curban forestry,\u201d \u201curban forest,\u201d and \u201cUrban Tree Canopy,\u201d and transfers \u00a7 1011 to \u00a7 1001 consistent with current legislative drafting guidance."
